    </div>

    <div class="footer__bottom">
      <div>
        <p>&copy; {year} The Vogt Real Estate Group. All rights reserved. DRE #02144449</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.72rem; opacity: 0.6; max-width: 640px;">
          All information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed and should be independently verified.
          All properties are subject to prior sale, change, or withdrawal.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer__eho">
        <img src="/images/realtor-eho-logo.png" alt="Equal Housing Opportunity and REALTOR logos" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
